# Seed Data Standards

Maintain realistic dev dataset via `python manage.py seed_demo_data`.

## Must seed

Super Admins, Admins, Election Officers, Students, Candidates, Demo Elections/Positions/Candidates, Demo Votes, Fraud Cases, Security Alerts, Results, Strongroom Records, Notifications.

## Data style

- Realistic Ghanaian names and TTU-style institution data
- Student index numbers: `BC/ITS/24/047`, `BC/ITD/24/031`, `BC/ITN/24/112`, `BC/ICT/24/056` — support any valid programme code, never hardcode prefixes only
- Document dev passwords in the management command docstring only — never hardcode credentials for production
